{"article_id":"qzg43zz2tQL0n4X2","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Daniel Snyder bought the Washington Redskins in 1999","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"but he has never faced as much pressure","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"to change the name of the team","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"as he is facing now ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"when symbols and statues of the country 's past have been torn down or removed amid heightened scrutiny","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"about what those things really mean .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"The Redskins name has been a source of controversy for about a month now ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"as politicians , media and now corporate sponsors have all asked Snyder to do without the name","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"that has been a part of the organization since 1933 ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"when the team was originally named the Boston Redskins .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"NIKE PULLS WASHINGTON REDSKINS APPAREL FROM ITS WEBSITE AMID TEAM NAME CONTROVERSY","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"In 2014 , Snyder told ESPN","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"that he wasn ' t going to succumb to pressure","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"to change the name","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"because he felt","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"that the term \" Redskins \" wasn ' t disparaging to Native Americans","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"but rather was a term","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"that dignified them with honor and respect .","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"He also pointed to two Native Americans","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"- William Henry \" Lone Star \" Dietz ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"whom the team was named after","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"to honor his heritage ,","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"and Walter \" Blackie \" Wetzel , a former Native American leader","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"who helped design and approve the team ' s logo .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"\" It 's just historical truths ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"and I 'd like them to understand ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"as I think","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"most do ,","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"that the name really means honor , respect , \"","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"he told ESPN at the time .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"\" We sing 'Hail to the Redskins . '","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"We do n't say","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"hurt anybody .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"We say 'Hail to the Redskins .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Braves on the warpath .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"Fight for old D.C. '","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"We only sing it","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"when we score touchdowns . \"","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"When asked what a \" Redskin \" was ,","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"Snyder replied :","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"\" A Redskin is a football player .","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"A Redskin is our fans .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"The Washington Redskins fan base represents honor ,","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"represents respect ,","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"represents pride .","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"Hopefully winning .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"And , and , it , it 's a positive .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Taken out of context ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"you can take things out of context all over the place .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"But in this particular case , it is what it is .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"It 's very obvious . \"","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"WASHINGTON REDSKINS SPONSORS PRESSURED TO CUT TIES","depth":4},{"id":52,"text":"UNLESS TEAM CHANGES NAMES","depth":4},{"id":53,"text":"In that same year , 50 senators agreed","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"that the Redskins should change their name .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"One letter to Roger Goodell asked the NFL Commissioner to push the organization to rename the team","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"citing the NBA ' s push","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"to remove Donald Sterling as the owner of the Los Angeles Clippers","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"when he was heard spouting racist remarks in a recording .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"\" We urge you and the National Football League to send the same clear message","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"as the NBA did :","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"that racism and bigotry have no place in professional sports , \"","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"senators wrote at the time .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Snyder told USA Today in 2013","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"the team would \" never change the name of the team . \"","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"\" As a lifelong Redskins fan , and I think","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"that the Redskins fans understand the great tradition and what it 's all about and what it means ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"so we feel pretty fortunate to be just working on next season , \"","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"he told the newspaper .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"He added :","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"\" We 'll never change the name .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"It 's that simple .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"NEVER -","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"you can use caps . \"","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"Admittedly , the social climate was different six and seven years ago .","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"Things appeared to start changing in the beginning of 2020 .","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"Recent public opinion polls appear to favor the Redskins name ,","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"and a University of California , Berkeley study","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"published in February","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"that at least half of the Native Americans","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"surveyed","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"were offended by the term .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"The publishers of the study were adamant about their results ,","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"according to WUSA9 .","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"Previous polls from The Washington Post , among others , had shown","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"that Americans weren ' t offended by the name .","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"REDSKINS CAN NOT MOVE TO NEW STADIUM","depth":4},{"id":88,"text":"UNLESS TEAM NAME CHANGES :","depth":4},{"id":89,"text":"REPORT","depth":3},{"id":90,"text":"The shift in public opinion seems connected to the May 25 death of George Floyd , the Minneapolis man","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"who died","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"after an officer kneeled on his neck for more than 8 minutes in a moment","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"caught on cellphone video .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"The Redskins team posted a black square on its Twitter page","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"to show solidarity with the Black Lives Matter movement .","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez , D-N.Y. , was among those","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"who called out the team to change the team name","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"if they were really supporting the call for social justice .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"Two weeks later , The Washington Post editorial board called on the team to change the name ,","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"despite its own 2016 polling revealing","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"that Americans weren ' t offended by the name .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"\" This should be an easy call .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"Mr. Snyder","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"- or ,","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"if Mr. Snyder refuses to back down from his declaration of \" NEVER , \" the NFL -","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"should take advantage of this singular moment in history","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"to get on the right side of history , \"","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"the newspaper said .","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"\" Change the name .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"NOW . \"","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"Even as the calls grew louder ,","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"the Redskins ' wallet was never really threatened - until this week .","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"The team is looking to move to a new stadium in the near future ,","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"but their relocation from Maryland to the RFK Stadium in D.C. now hinges on the organization ' s willingness","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"to change its name ,","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"The Washington Post reported on Wednesday .","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"On Thursday , FedEx publicly requested","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"that the Redskins change their name .","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"Making things more interesting ,","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"FedEx CEO Fred Smith is also the minority owner of the organization .","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"Nike also appeared to remove Redskins gear from its website .","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"Merchandise disappeared","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"one day after a group of 87 investment firms sent letters to three of the Redskins ' prominent corporate sponsors .","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"Nike , FedEx and PepsiCo were urged to pressure Washington team officials to change the name and to end their business relationships with the franchise","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"if ownership would not comply .","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"Washington has not commented on the recent developments","depth":5},{"id":127,"text":"but one thing is for sure :","depth":6},{"id":128,"text":"the calls","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"for the team","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"to change their name","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"have never been louder","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"than they are now .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":265,"left":219,"right":264,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":219,"left":183,"right":218,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":183,"left":143,"right":182,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":142,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":138,"right":141,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":138,"left":0,"right":137,"relation